{"tid":1316840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【帶領輿論】由強調自己手無寸鐵，升級至以武制暴嘅正當性！！！","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T08:12:40.000Z","uid":2010,"like":182,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"76203dcde2cc816a1c489aa9e7d59f50cd05696c","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">面對呢個不義政權，以武力反抗係唯一而正當手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n過往嘅文宣大多強調示威者<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手無寸鐵</span></strong>，但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仍然遭到警察無理、殘暴嘅鎮壓</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n當越嚟越多勇武派出手、以及和理非轉而支持勇武嘅時候，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋係時候主動出擊，將輿論升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武抗爭已經成為必然而且<span style=\"color: red;\">正義</span>嘅手段</span></strong>，</span><br />\n因為我哋係阻止緊政權去殘害香港人嘅兄弟姊妹，<br />\n同時喺和理非遭受打壓嘅基礎上，<br />\n為以武制暴嘅前線增加社會大眾嘅支持。</span><br />\n<br />\n與此同時，請繼續<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">渲染警察嘅失控、暴戾行為</span></strong>，<br />\n追打示威者、記者、議員以及途人，<br />\n逼到青年跳橋、將示威者剝光豬再拘捕等等等等嘅行為，<br />\n務求令以武制暴嘅手段嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正當性</span></span></strong>得到認同！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非Cover勇武派，勇武派喺和理非嘅支持下走上最前線，</span></span><br />\n咁先係真正嘅兄弟爬山，齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家加油！！！</span>"},{"pid":"539bf54c6bb0abc07b7d2534eee4e767fe3e7ad3","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"推！！！！<br />\n唔使再話自己冇打過警察、冇警察受傷，<br />\n而係要講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日警察比示威者反擊，係合理而正當嘅反抗，係佢哋自己造成！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecd9c9562195e37d8e314d050086df0a9900868","tid":1316840,"uid":238051,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">你扮警察\n有人冒警\n我冇嘢講\n我要搵律師</code></pre>"},{"pid":"77a3789d1732c4755147a9c1909d65d402c6c13f","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:57:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔使話：冇警察受傷<br />\n試下講：係警察將示威者逼到要用武力反抗！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"bd7a889c6fb64e84549b84f006f7f7ec6df23175","tid":1316840,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"文宣攻保皇：前線警中矢之的，偽建制派議員全部失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316637</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e7415b6b6c41d7351f49b61677ee3cb5f829aa9","tid":1316840,"uid":224095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"唔係警察包抄，香港人點會勇武。"},{"pid":"931f09d14b93bf8c3264009e7c58ff0cc81fa926","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:00:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係警察將曾經和平嘅示威者逼到要用武力反抗！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"04dad23b21f1004ebbfdfb7c4a9be3b5384affb4","tid":1316840,"uid":162095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"同意，無必要美化咁多嘢<br />\n講光環，6月已經夠"},{"pid":"fc70d7ba6374f3cce587ee0218638f8e02e36c8c","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04dad23b21f1004ebbfdfb7c4a9be3b5384affb4","tid":1316840,"uid":162095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"同意，無必要美化咁多嘢<br />\n講光環，6月已經夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔需要再包裝自己係和平，</span><br />\n因為咁樣同時係強調緊自己唔夠強硬，<br />\n要強調係政權逼到我哋要咁樣反抗，<br />\n官逼民反，<br />\n再多警察比示威者攻擊，都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政權自己造成嘅後果</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf69616b53210eb102b0a6e072e51c953156ea3","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋唔係咩手無寸鐵嘅學生，<br />\n我哋係<strong>正當地以武力反抗不義政權嘅香港人</strong>！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c269fbf27b44a3c4551e4b3e7700eadac05adc","tid":1316840,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;我無嘢講"},{"pid":"8706359e1d26fb91e942b46aefaec9ac653672d5","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"唔需要再包裝自己係和平，<br />\n個幾月嚟和平嘅場面已經夠晒多，<br />\n我哋要做嘅係，<br />\n令社會大眾認同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武派反擊嘅正當性</span></span>！！！"},{"pid":"80bc05e9a28633bcc04abbd7e81f3a8bf4e1002d","tid":1316840,"uid":275963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pi