剋制，多次警告警察要出示委任證，並開路以讓示威者散去<br />\n可惜，警察依然停滯不前，不利勸預，實屬遺憾<br />\n經多方勸預後，示威者決定使用合理武力制服疑似武警暴徒<br />\n就警方今日嘅暴力行爲，香港人表示極度遺憾，並予以強力譴責」"},{"pid":"6782c8245c8d6c7ede4a4cbd14ea73571025d67e","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>雙管齊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉自<strong>高學歷廢青巴</strong>嘅Post：<br />\n「示威者已經好剋制，多次警告警察要出示委任證，並開路以讓示威者散去<br />\n可惜，警察依然停滯不前，不利勸預，實屬遺憾<br />\n經多方勸預後，示威者決定使用合理武力制服疑似武警暴徒<br />\n就警方今日嘅暴力行爲，香港人表示極度遺憾，並予以強力譴責」</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2c1b5be80d23666ad16d93726552bfe239d48e38","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:27:58.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山嘅真諦，唔單止係各自努力，<br />\n更加要互相Cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當和理非遭到殘暴打壓，勇武派出手就係正義、正當之舉！</span>"},{"pid":"aaad21c1cece38a5a19b0e439188dec2fcdc0bd0","tid":1316840,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dce62860667a2e51a3656ce579ba12c462bcd2b","tid":1316840,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0bf8c93fc72692d6cfa9e9b911b399de51daebf","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"有唔少巴打都提到，<br />\n將輿論引導去<strong>因為示威者思疑有人冒警</strong>，<br />\n所以先用武力嘗試制服冒警人士。<br />\n<br />\n呢個論點唔係唔得，<br />\n但好明顯前線係因為警察以至政權嘅不義而反抗，<br />\n將以武制暴嘅行為spin去因為思疑有人冒警，<br />\n只能夠呃自己，但呃唔到出面呃嘅人，<br />\n唔足夠令社會大眾支持示威者反擊，<br />\n所以最大目標，一定係提升反抗嘅正當性，<br />\n亦即係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">明知你係警察，亦明知你係代表不義政權，<br />\n我哋先更加要還擊，用武力對抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"06e7dcb5a9128d50ca07491e91104da36115ebb0","tid":1316840,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"和平是市民將就俾咗handicap。<br />\n9. 瓦解逆民之權無罪。You may dissolve a power that opposes the people.<br />\n【無大台攻略】歡迎來玩民主世界遊戲！<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299957</a>"},{"pid":"a36bd0ccc9f4e67729f865acae095c0e00012322","tid":1316840,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9a05ff26bd67dd8e01ff43d79f3f90434ce7fa86","tid":1316840,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06e7dcb5a9128d50ca07491e91104da36115ebb0","tid":1316840,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"和平是市民將就俾咗handicap。<br />\n9. 瓦解逆民之權無罪。You may dissolve a power that opposes the people.<br />\n【無大台攻略】歡迎來玩民主世界遊戲！<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299957</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:43:59.000Z","msg":"8. 阻止逆民之舉無罪。You may stop an act that opposes the people.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48e1d680b2da4afac1247d5519447163bde6e77","tid":1316840,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a05ff26bd67dd8e01ff43d79f3f90434ce7fa86","tid":1316840,"uid":2010